source: crates/biome_formatter_test/src/snapshot_builder.rs
info: yaml/spec/spec-example-6-1-indentation-spaces.yml
---

# Input

```yml
  # Leading comment line spaces are
   # neither content nor indentation.
    
Not indented:
 By one space: |
    By four
      spaces
 Flow style: [    # Leading spaces
   By two,        # in flow style
  Also by two,    # are neither
  	Still by two   # content nor
    ]             # indentation.

```


# Prettier differences

```diff
--- Prettier
+++ Biome
@@ -5,8 +5,9 @@
   By one space: |
     By four
       spaces
-  Flow style: # Leading spaces
+  Flow style:
     [
+      # Leading spaces
       By two, # in flow style
       Also by two, # are neither
       Still by two, # content nor
```

# Output

```yml
# Leading comment line spaces are
# neither content nor indentation.

Not indented:
  By one space: |
    By four
      spaces
  Flow style:
    [
      # Leading spaces
      By two, # in flow style
      Also by two, # are neither
      Still by two, # content nor
    ] # indentation.
```
